ElementDescription: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject
Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project
Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY
Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging.
Notes: Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.
M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

ElementDescription: How much does your/ your child's illness/developmental concerns affect your life?
Notes: 0=no affect at all; 10=severely affects my life; 99=Missing value

ElementDescription: How long do you think your/your child's illness/developmental concerns will continue?
Notes: 0=no affect at all; 10=severely affects my life; 99=Missing value

ElementDescription: How much control do you feel you have over your/your child illness/developmental concerns?
Notes: 0=no affect at all; 10=severely affects my life; 99=Missing value

ElementDescription: How much do you think your/ your child's treatment can help your/his/her illness/developmental concerns?
Notes: 0=no affect at all; 10=severely affects my life; 99=Missing value

ElementDescription: How much do you/your child experience symptoms from your/your child's illness/developmental concerns?
Notes: 0=no affect at all; 10=severely affects my life; 99=Missing value

ElementDescription: How concerned are you about your/your child' illness?
Notes: 0=no affect at all; 10=severely affects my life; 99=Missing value

ElementDescription: How well do you feel you understand your/ your child's illness/developmental concerns?
Notes: 0=no affect at all; 10=severely affects my life; 99=Missing value

ElementDescription: How much does your/your child's aillness/developmental concerns affect you emotionally? (e.g. does it make you angry, scared, upset, or depressed?)
Notes: 0=no affect at all; 10=severely affects my life; 99=Missing value

ElementDescription: Compared to one year ago, how prepared do you feel to manage your/your child's illness/developmental needs?
Notes: 0=no affect at all; 10=severely affects my life; 99=Missing value

ElementDescription: How much do you share your/your child's illness/developmental diagnosis with other people such as friends and family members?
Notes: 0=no affect at all; 10=severely affects my life; 99=Missing value
